        "description": "Galactic Drift is a high-speed sci-fi racing game where you race against 16 other pilots for the biggest bounty in the galaxy! Anything goes as you use weapons and crazy tricks to defeat your rivals. \n\nWhat is Galactic Drift?\n\nThe best way to describe it would be as an on-rails sci-fi racing game but you still have full control over the steering of your spacecraft around a tunnel. You will use the Oculus control grip buttons to reach forward and grab the steering wheel while turning the wheel will see you spin left and right around the racing tunnel, avoiding hazards and other craft. You collect weapons along the route to try and destroy your rival racers, while racing to win.\n\nWhat’s in the Demo\n\n⦾ High- quality graphics (not final)\n\n⦾ Immersive controls.\n\n⦾ Take control of the Storm Racing ship. (More coming soon.)\n\n⦾ Weapon pick-ups.\n\n⦾ Shield pick-ups\n\n⦾ 3x Single races.\n\n⦾ 1x 3 race tour",
